{"tid":722497,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【乘客小心！】乘客指責兇徒「變態 」 會摸下張凳先坐","createTime":"2018-06-29T14:30:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-29T17:31:39.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d979607af2edd2675014354e68cf35250c417b7f","tid":722497,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T14:30:22.000Z","msg":"九巴一日內發生3宗座位暗藏鐵針事件，導致兩名女乘客被刺傷臀部及大腿，今晨又有一名男乘客乘坐17號線巴士，落車後發現褲袋鈎著大頭針，通知站長代為報警，幸他未有受傷。但事件已令乘客不安。乘搭17號線的郭先生指事件曝光後自己會小心，「坐低前會摸下張凳有冇針先坐」。而李小姐則斥責兇徒「變態」，並表示搭巴士會加緊留意，「平時會直接坐喺凳，依家會留意。」<br />\n<br />\n經常搭17號線的盧小姐，聽到又有乘客差點被刺針拮傷，即表現「驚愕」，「以前坐低未必會摸下座位，冇留意，真係好危險」，她對事件感擔心。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/29/222923_62ca238fd269afe33dbaf848ac750df9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F29%2F222923_62ca238fd269afe33dbaf848ac750df9.png&h=1e2243ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n盧小姐對刺針事件感擔心,及覺得很危險。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/29/222946_da233901cb1ccf5fd4d997b45b01fdc0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F29%2F222946_da233901cb1ccf5fd4d997b45b01fdc0.png&h=8d6446a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n李小姐指兇徒變態。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180629/58378194\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180629%2F58378194&d=IRc0hK8F%2FdEAD2QkKYcFmwKEmdudW1rq3V1Y15kzxIU%3D&h=d6ac41f7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180629%2F58378194&h=e0eeebd7\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180629/58378194</a>"},{"pid":"4e17fff251b0192e5109ecc7384d2bafcea28963","tid":722497,"uid":132587,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-29T14:34:09.000Z","msg":"平時專登坐係你地隔離d呀伯仲變態啦<img src=\"/asse